data.meta_description: Marine Barracks Washington celebrates its 221st Birthday on March 31, 2022. Barracks alumni came back to MBW to share some of their favorite stories and give their take on the importance and impact of the Barracks
data.text: Marine Barracks Washington celebrates its 221st Birthday on March 31, 2022. Barracks alumni came back to MBW to share some of their favorite stories and give their take on the importance and impact of the Barracks' mission. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpls. Tanner D. Lambert and Mark A. Morales)
